OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers will fade away,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry evening with
OL,8,Flight winds. Cloud will increase from
OL,9,Fthe west later, bringing a few
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain before dawn. Winds
OL,11,Ffreshening later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloud and rain gradually
OL,14,Ftransferring north-eastwards through
OL,15,Fthe morning. Some brighter intervals
OL,16,Fdevelop for a time, but further heavy
OL,17,Fafternoon showers following, perhaps
OL,18,Fthundery. Breezy inland, strong
OL,19,Fcoastal winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
